    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "2.   In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—",
      "content": "2.   In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“child”  includes  a  step-child  and  a  child  adopted  by  the  recipient \nunder  any  written  law  relating  to  adoption,  or  under  any  custom  or \nusage;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Decoration”  means  the  Decoration  of  Panglima  Gagah  Berani \nconferred  under  the  Statutes  of  Panglima  Gagah  Berani  (P.G.B.) \n[G.N. 3151/1960];",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“remembrance  allowance”  means  the  remembrance  allowance",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_63",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "granted under subsection 3(1);",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_64",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6                                        Laws of Malaysia                           ACT 616",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_65",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“spouse”  means  the  widow  or  widower  of  a  deceased  recipient \nwhose  marriage  is recognized  in Malaysia as a valid  marriage under \nany written law, religion, custom or usage;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_66",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“recipient” means a person who has been conferred the Decoration.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_67",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant of remembrance allowance",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_68",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3.   (1)   There  may  be  granted  to  a  recipient  of  a  Decoration  a \nremembrance  allowance  of  one  thousand  and  five  hundred  ringgit  a \nmonth, and where the Decoration is conferred on such recipient more \nthan  once,  there  may  be  granted  to  him  a  separate  remembrance \nallowance  of  one  thousand  and  five  hundred  ringgit  a  month  in \nrespect of each Decoration conferred on him.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_69",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)   The  remembrance  allowance  shall  be  payable  in  arrear  no",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_70",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "earlier than the end of each month.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_71",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)   Where",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_72",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "the  Decoration  was",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_73",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "the \ncommencement  of  this  Act  and  the  recipient  is  living  upon  such \ncommencement, \nremembrance  allowance  shall  be  paid \nretrospectively to the recipient, commencing with the month in which \nthe  Decoration  was  conferred  on  him,  but  not  earlier,  in  any  case, \nthan the month of June 1983.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
