      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_92",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  upon  the  cancellation  or  annulment  of  the  conferment  of \nthe  Decoration  in  accordance  with  section  VIII  of  the \nStatutes of Panglima Gagah Berani.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_93",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)   No  remembrance  allowance  shall  be  paid  commencing  with \nthe  month  in  which  the  death  of  the  recipient  takes  place,  or  the \nsentence  is  imposed  on  the  recipient,  or  the  conferment  of  the \nDecoration is cancelled or annulled, as the case may be.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_94",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)   For  the  purposes  of  subsection  (2),  the  month  in  which  the \nsentence  is  imposed  means  the  month  in  which  the  sentence  is \npronounced  by  the  trial  court  or  if  there  is  an  appeal  against  such \nsentence  the  month  in  which  such  sentence  is  confirmed  on  such \nappeal.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_95",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(4)   If  the  recipient  receives  a  free  pardon  in  respect  of  such \nconviction,  or  if  the  cancelled  or  annulled  Decoration  is  restored  to \nhim, \nto  him \ncommencing from the month in which the free pardon is received or \nthe Decoration is restored.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_96",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "the  remembrance  allowance  shall  be  restored",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_97",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant  to  next-of-kin  of  recipient  where  Decoration  is  conferred \nposthumously",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_98",
      "heading": "5.   (1)   Where  the  Decoration  has  been  conferred  posthumously \nbefore the commencement of this Act, there may be made a grant of a \ntotal sum of fifteen thousand ringgit once only—",
      "content": "5.   (1)   Where  the  Decoration  has  been  conferred  posthumously \nbefore the commencement of this Act, there may be made a grant of a \ntotal sum of fifteen thousand ringgit once only—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_99",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a) to  the  spouse  or  spouses  and  children  of  the  deceased \nrecipient who are living on the date of the commencement \nof this Act;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_100",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b) if on the date of the commencement of this Act no spouse \nor child of the deceased recipient  is  living, to the parents \nor parent of the deceased recipient who are or is living on \nsuch date; or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_101",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "8                                        Laws of Malaysia                           ACT 616",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_102",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  if on the date of the commencement of this Act no spouse, \nchild  or  parent  of  the  deceased  recipient  is  living,  to  the \ngrandparents or grandparent of the deceased recipient who \nare or is living on such date.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_103",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  Where  the  Decoration  is  conferred  posthumously  after  the \ncommencement of this Act, there may be made a grant of a total sum \nof fifteen thousand ringgit once only—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_104",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a) to  the  spouse  or  spouses  and  children  of  the  deceased \nrecipient who are  living on the date of the conferment of \nthe Decoration;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_105",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b) if  on  the  date  of  the  conferment  of  the  Decoration  no \nspouse  or  child  of  the  deceased  recipient  is  living, to the \nparents  or  parent  of  the  deceased  recipient  who  are  or  is \nliving on such date; or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_106",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  if  on  the  date  of  the  conferment  of  the  Decoration  no \nspouse, child or parent of the deceased recipient is living, \nto  the  grandparents  or  grandparent  of  the  deceased \nrecipient who are or is living on such date.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_107",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant \ncommencement of Act",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_108",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "to  next-of-kin  of  recipient  who  had  died  before",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_109",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6.  Where the Decoration was conferred before the commencement of \nthis  Act  and  the  recipient  had  died  before  the  date  of  such \ncommencement, there may be made a grant of a total sum of fifteen \nthousand ringgit once only—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_110",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a) to  the  spouse  or  spouses  and  children  of  the  deceased \nrecipient who are living on the date of the commencement \nof this Act;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_111",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b) if on the date of the commencement of this Act no spouse \nor child of the deceased recipient  is  living, to the parents",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_112",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Panglima Gagah Berani (Remembrance Allowance)                 9",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_113",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "or parent of the deceased recipient who are or is living on \nsuch date; or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_114",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  if on the date of the commencement of this Act no spouse, \nchild  or  parent  of  the  deceased  recipient  is  living,  to  the \ngrandparents or grandparent of the deceased recipient who \nare or is living on such date.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_115",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Prime Minister to apportion amount to be paid",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_116",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "7.   The amount to be paid to the spouse or spouses, children, parents \nor grandparents, as the case may be, under section 5 or 6 shall be in \nsuch proportions as may be determined by the Prime Minister.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_117",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Remembrance  allowance  and  sum  to  be  charged  to  the  Federal \nConsolidated Fund",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_118",
      "heading": "8.   The  remembrance  allowance  and  sums  granted  under  this  Act \nshall be charged to the Federal Consolidated Fund.",
      "content": "8.   The  remembrance  allowance  and  sums  granted  under  this  Act \nshall be charged to the Federal Consolidated Fund.",
      "section_number": null,
